間尺咁直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小朋友 <br />\n欣賞你咁有好奇心<br />\n睇下咩叫彈墨<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C2ce8cjru5Y?t=25s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC2ce8cjru5Y%3Ft%3D25s&d=1egFhdo94ZcAly336djUofjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=f6f23b28\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/C2ce8cjru5Y?t=25s</a>?t=25s<br />\n拉直條線其實直過用尺</blockquote><br />\n唔明點解拉線會直過尺</blockquote><br />\n因為如果你用尺畫長距離嘅直線，你會有好多因素影響，例如 手震，石屎地嘅凹凸，撞到把尺等等。。加上你要蹲低畫有辛苦，好易唔直或者兩截，唔係你可以畫條4m以上嘅直線<br />\n<br />\n用墨斗線拉緊其實好穩</blockquote><br />\n因為線就係由2個受力既點拉直而成 兩個點拉實會成直線呢個係定律來 一把尺冇可能永遠保持筆直 因為佢上面既直其實係由好多個點組成 而呢D點係可以因為製造質素，或者係損耗做成個別移位<br />\n而不論你用幼線定粗繩 只要佢有2個點拉扯受緊力 就冇可能唔直"},{"pid":"921970f19ba3ce32748671c15e9749f889534ea4","tid":427216,"uid":59179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T20:46:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好似講尺點嚟變咗cm點嚟？</blockquote><br />\n唔好意思 比我騎劫左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f717a1b4c84d97742f8c57517848941b156151","tid":427216,"uid":35606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T20:46:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>光一秒行3x10^8km<br />\n<br />\n之後點整唔洗我講喇</blockquote><br />\n小學畢業未？"},{"pid":"d55d533d22dcd9c138ae10190b326d70fa0a233b","tid":427216,"uid":58147,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T21:32:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>古時將赤道同北極係地球表面嘅距離定義做一萬公里，再將一公里除返一千就係一米<br />\n<br />\n利申： 航海course學</blockquote><br />\n航海唔係用海里㗎咩？<br />\n考你，<br />\n一海里係點嚟？"},{"pid":"5e56efefd2e40932fdc98a26a528629de5e56371","tid":427216,"uid":12348,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T01:46:29.000Z","msg":"其實上面話「有條友鳩噏一條線就係1m，然後除100就有1cm」呢個說法應該唔啱。<br />\n其實嗰一條線唔一定要係整數，可以俾100整除。求其一個數字都可以分成100份，只係結果唔係一個整數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad22890487fe920290d2d809dec9d077f00989f","tid":427216,"uid":126083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T02:09:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>古時將赤道同北極係地球表面嘅距離定義做一萬公里，再將一公里除返一千就係一米<br />\n<br />\n利申： 航海course學</blockquote><br />\n航海唔係用海里㗎咩？<br />\n考你，<br />\n一海里係點嚟？</blockquote><br />\n以前就係講緊緯度線嘅1/16&deg;<br />\n但SI基本上統一晒所有單位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家變咗用米做定義<br />\n正如Fahrenheit同Kelvin依家都係base on Celsius嚟定義<br />\n又或者Miles, cm, foot, etc都係用米嚟定義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f2a210fed79aa797917c0e00483b4c3ed16131","tid":427216,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T02:23:05.000Z","msg":"定義嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afdb79359e5678a8d56788baab3abae8ed7979c6","tid":427216,"uid":117647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T02:41:53.000Z","msg":"咁世界上第一個對一秒既定義呢？"},{"pid":"1d0a0c4c70627b3f68bc452734157c7c3b8ef6f4","tid":427216,"uid":84228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T03:05:07.000Z","msg":"手中無尺，心中有尺<br />\n<br />\n不過認真想問古時係點樣計到m同cm，同埋古時木工點整到咁直"},{"pid":"b36fe931a465dd517702ae8cb0f738fb868072ab","tid":427216,"uid":17368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T03:16:27.000Z","msg":"其實好簡單，你搵樣嘢做參照物（例如搵塊木，再切成小長方形木板），叫佢做1cm，然後用塊木板去量，咪整到尺囉。（即係係塊大板上面，用同一塊木牌量，每1cm就用筆劃線，塊木牌再移後一格，想把尺幾長就量幾次）"},{"pid":"c90f1b8810159bc10569893332d50a4f2dcc028e","tid":427216,"uid":61510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T04:16:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一個翻譯家係點做到？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83beb9613be77ce802907ddbfcc4ccccfa377ee7","tid":427216,"uid":11694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T04:20:48.000Z","msg":"地球上第一個1cm係點出黎?"},{"pid":"56e161d0a93712724ddafdefe3f66eb8ebada3c9","tid":427216,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T04:22:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第一個翻譯家係點做到？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n身體語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5e8779a1e6bdd56608c3465fd27414862e5361","tid":427216,"uid":20001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T04:29:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>全世界第一把尺是公輸班（因是春秋魯國人,又稱為：魯班）發明的,魯班從小就喜歡觀察事物,舉凡大人煮飯、砍材、蓋房子,連牛在吃草都看得很仔細。他不僅認真看,還用心的想,常常做出精巧有用的東西。長大後他成為一名出色的木匠。為了在木材上畫直線,他發明了『墨斗』。但是,一開始用墨斗放線時,他總是得請母親拉緊線的另一端,才能把線畫好。後來他做了一個彎鉤,把線的另一端鉤在木材上,就可以取代手拉線,一個人操作便能畫好直線了。</blockquote><br />\n其實魯班都幾撚醒<br />\n如果係依家佢應該係個D裝修地盤工人<br />\n但就咁好唸頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港座魯班先師廟就係地盤佬起出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊座廟唔係地盤佬起出黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a2e815164b7d31d5ed2643d1f35d312161eb87","tid":427216,"uid":71376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T04:37:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>古時將赤道同北極係地球表面嘅距離定義做一萬公里，再將一公里除返一千就係一米<br />\n<br />\n利申： 航海course學</blockquote><br />\n航海唔係用海里㗎咩？<br />\n考你，<br />\n一海里係點嚟？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1 minute of latitude"},{"pid":"952948e7b96db5954108ae980b91e1b62b05285e","tid":427216,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:07:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我個人係覺得有米(m)先過厘米(cm)<br />\n因為英文都好, 都係將唔同嘅si unit 放喺m 前面代表mm cm km etc.<br />\n不過點定義就冇諗法, lm 學野</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://lmgtfy.com/?q=si+base+unit+wiki\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flmgtfy.com%2F%3Fq%3Dsi%2Bbase%2Bunit%2Bwiki&d=1egFhdo94ZcAly336djUofjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=9df0f0f8\" target=\"_blank\">http://lmgtfy.com/?q=si+base+unit+wiki</a>"},{"pid":"7a7ffd94f1fd81149bf7bc459d048ba1abbead92","tid":427216,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:21:04.000Z","msg":"至於間尺<br />\n首先有直尺 其實係任何有直邊嘅物體都得<br />\n之後有人屎忽痕放咗啲刻度上去<br />\n咁為咗慳材料就造成而家嘅長方形"},{"pid":"a7c51b53df4d47153c65bc8653f3ee4146a28750","tid":427216,"uid":112741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:43:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>古時將赤道同北極係地球表面嘅距離定義做一萬公里，再將一公里除返一千就係一米<br />\n<br />\n利申： 航海course學</blockquote><br />\n航海唔係用海里㗎咩？<br />\n考你，<br />\n一海里係點嚟？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n地球surface 1 minute，完"},{"pid":"eb73b30f63ae8b0f9f3b7c0d271269b2221f1d01","tid":427216,"uid":112741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:49:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>古時將赤道同北極係地球表面嘅距離定義做一萬公里，再將一公里除返一千就係一米<br />\n<br />\n利申： 航海course學</blockquote><br />\n航海唔係用海里㗎咩？<br />\n考你，<br />\n一海里係點嚟？</blockquote><br />\n講開海里點黎咪順便講埋米囉，都係同一個方法定義出黎嘅<br />\n你唔信咪自己查下地球南北圓周係咪大約40000km"},{"pid":"370f1c9ff742716e356ce729ba5bb1542bb6a640","tid":427216,"uid":12232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T06:16:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>光一秒行3x10^8km<br />\n<br />\n之後點整唔洗我講喇</blockquote><br />\n翻去溫書啦，km都講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪應該3x10^8m/s<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔記得喇頂 脫離左讀書好耐</blockquote><br />\n唔記得就咪拋書包<br />\n拋完錯左又話好耐未掂過，是鳩旦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好撚柒呀媽呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f67bedd132d8df80c5f5e55bca89c376d6d16baa","tid":427216,"uid":77092,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T07:06:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6eeb1abffe3d115b44f0b976bdf9700fece92dcb","tid":427216,"uid":82452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T07:08:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未有人製造一款標準既間尺既時候<br />\n係點樣整到咁直咁標準既間尺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"}]}